{"word":"νόσημα","slug":"νόσημα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>νόσημα</b></el> <el>(νόσημα, ατος, τό,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:νοσέω'><el>νοσέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a sickness, disease, plague</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>disease, affliction</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b>of <i>disorder</i> in a state, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}